{
  "video_id": "8v_GrrQs8ow",
  "title": "We can fight terror without sacrificing our rights | Rebecca MacKinnon",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12888.0,
      "end_time": 15220.0,
      "text": "There's a big question at the center of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15460.0,
      "end_time": 16960.0,
      "text": "in our democracies today:"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16984.0,
      "end_time": 20329.0,
      "text": "How do we fight terror without destroying democracies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20353.0,
      "end_time": 22876.0,
      "text": "without trampling human rights?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23594.0,
      "end_time": 28189.0,
      "text": "I've spent much of my career working with journalists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28213.0,
      "end_time": 29371.0,
      "text": "with bloggers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29395.0,
      "end_time": 30709.0,
      "text": "with activists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30733.0,
      "end_time": 33348.0,
      "text": "with human rights researchers all around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33372.0,
      "end_time": 35482.0,
      "text": "and I've come to the conclusion"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35506.0,
      "end_time": 40150.0,
      "text": "that if our democratic societies do not double down"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40175.0,
      "end_time": 43157.0,
      "text": "on protecting and defending human rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43182.0,
      "end_time": 44582.0,
      "text": "freedom of the press"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44606.0,
      "end_time": 47220.0,
      "text": "and a free and open internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47932.0,
      "end_time": 53793.0,
      "text": "radical extremist ideologies are much more likely to persist."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54537.0,
      "end_time": 56982.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57600.0,
      "end_time": 58690.0,
      "text": "OK, all done. Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58714.0,
      "end_time": 59873.0,
      "text": "No, just joking."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59897.0,
      "end_time": 61306.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61716.0,
      "end_time": 64608.0,
      "text": "I actually want to drill down on this a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64965.0,
      "end_time": 70712.0,
      "text": "So, one of the countries that has been on the frontlines of this issue"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70736.0,
      "end_time": 71966.0,
      "text": "is Tunisia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72325.0,
      "end_time": 75841.0,
      "text": "which was the only country to come out of the Arab Spring"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75865.0,
      "end_time": 78463.0,
      "text": "with a successful democratic revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78967.0,
      "end_time": 80232.0,
      "text": "Five years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80256.0,
      "end_time": 83920.0,
      "text": "they're struggling with serious terror attacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83116.0,
      "end_time": 85829.0,
      "text": "and rampant ISIS recruitment."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85853.0,
      "end_time": 88637.0,
      "text": "And many Tunisians are calling on their government"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88661.0,
      "end_time": 91721.0,
      "text": "to do whatever it takes to keep them safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92686.0,
      "end_time": 95714.0,
      "text": "Tunisian cartoonist Nadia Khiari"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95738.0,
      "end_time": 100130.0,
      "text": "has summed up the situation with this character who says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 100370.0,
      "end_time": 102616.0,
      "text": "\"I don't give a damn about human rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102640.0,
      "end_time": 105491.0,
      "text": "I don't give a damn about the revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 105515.0,
      "end_time": 108971.0,
      "text": "I don't give a damn about democracy and liberty."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109587.0,
      "end_time": 111177.0,
      "text": "I just want to be safe.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113672.0,
      "end_time": 116140.0,
      "text": "\"Satisfied?\" asked his jailer."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116896.0,
      "end_time": 118205.0,
      "text": "\"You're safe now.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 118941.0,
      "end_time": 121696.0,
      "text": "If the Tunisian people can figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121720.0,
      "end_time": 123783.0,
      "text": "how to deal with their terrorism problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 123807.0,
      "end_time": 126229.0,
      "text": "without ending up in this place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 126771.0,
      "end_time": 129454.0,
      "text": "they will be a model not only for their region,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129478.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130846.00000000001,
      "text": "but for all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 132402.0,
      "end_time": 136438.0,
      "text": "The reality is that civil society, journalists and activists"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136462.0,
      "end_time": 141291.0,
      "text": "are coming under attack from extremist groups on the one hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141315.0,
      "end_time": 143450.0,
      "text": "and, in many countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143690.0,
      "end_time": 145504.0,
      "text": "also from their own governments."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 145528.0,
      "end_time": 148920.0,
      "text": "We're seeing bloggers and journalists being jailed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 148944.0,
      "end_time": 150381.0,
      "text": "charged and intimidated"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 150406.0,
      "end_time": 151924.0,
      "text": "by their own governments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 151948.0,
      "end_time": 155343.0,
      "text": "many of which are allies with the West in the war on terror."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 155785.0,
      "end_time": 157422.0,
      "text": "Just three examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 157446.0,
      "end_time": 159302.0,
      "text": "A friend and former colleague of mine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 159326.0,
      "end_time": 160558.0,
      "text": "Hisham Almiraat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 160582.0,
      "end_time": 163626.0,
      "text": "has been charged with threatening state security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 163650.0,
      "end_time": 166599.0,
      "text": "along with six other activists in Morocco."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 167144.0,
      "end_time": 171617.0,
      "text": "The Saudi blogger Raif Badawi has been jailed and flogged"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 171641.0,
      "end_time": 177412.0,
      "text": "for insulting Islam and criticizing the Saudi regime on his blog."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 177437.0,
      "end_time": 182927.0,
      "text": "More recently, the Turkish representative for Reporters Without Borders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182951.0,
      "end_time": 184798.0,
      "text": "Erol Ã–nderoglu,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 184822.0,
      "end_time": 189566.0,
      "text": "has been detained and charged with spreading terrorist propaganda,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 189590.0,
      "end_time": 194520.0,
      "text": "because he and some other activists have been supporting Kurdish media."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 195250.0,
      "end_time": 198712.0,
      "text": "Anti-terror measures quickly turn into state repression"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 198736.0,
      "end_time": 201811.0,
      "text": "without strong protection for minority communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202297.0,
      "end_time": 204338.0,
      "text": "and for peaceful debate;"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 204729.0,
      "end_time": 209725.0,
      "text": "this needs to be supported by a robust, independent local media."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 209749.0,
      "end_time": 212530.0,
      "text": "But while that's not really happening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 212770.0,
      "end_time": 216680.0,
      "text": "Washington is teaming up with Silicon Valley and with Hollywood"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 216701.0,
      "end_time": 221770.0,
      "text": "to pour millions -- hundreds of millions of dollars --"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221101.0,
      "end_time": 223688.0,
      "text": "into what's called \"counter-messaging,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223712.0,
      "end_time": 225691.0,
      "text": "a fancy word for propaganda."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 226154.0,
      "end_time": 232330.0,
      "text": "To counter the terrorist propaganda spreading all over the internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 232614.0,
      "end_time": 236360.0,
      "text": "in Europe, Internet Referral Units are being set up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 236384.0,
      "end_time": 240361.0,
      "text": "so that people can report on extremist content that they find"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 240385.0,
      "end_time": 241792.0,
      "text": "and get it censored."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 242191.0,
      "end_time": 243551.0,
      "text": "The problem is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 243575.0,
      "end_time": 248179.0,
      "text": "that all of this propaganda, monitoring and censorship"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 248204.0,
      "end_time": 252787.0,
      "text": "completely fails to make up for the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 253236.0,
      "end_time": 258310.0,
      "text": "that the people who are the most credible voices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 258334.0,
      "end_time": 262419.0,
      "text": "who can present credible ideas and alternative solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 262443.0,
      "end_time": 266544.0,
      "text": "to real economic, social and political problems in their community"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 266568.0,
      "end_time": 270851.0,
      "text": "that are causing people to turn to extremism in the first place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 270875.0,
      "end_time": 273691.0,
      "text": "are being silenced by their own governments."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 274214.0,
      "end_time": 278776.0,
      "text": "This is all adding up to a decrease in freedom across the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 279801.0,
      "end_time": 280977.0,
      "text": "Freedom House,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 281100.0,
      "end_time": 283300.0,
      "text": "the human rights organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 283550.0,
      "end_time": 287391.0,
      "text": "reports that 2015 marks the 10th straight year in a row"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 287415.0,
      "end_time": 290471.0,
      "text": "of decline in freedom worldwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 290495.0,
      "end_time": 292891.0,
      "text": "And this is not just because of the actions"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 292915.0,
      "end_time": 294946.0,
      "text": "of authoritarian governments."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 294970.0,
      "end_time": 297467.0,
      "text": "It's also because democratic governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 297491.0,
      "end_time": 301794.0,
      "text": "are increasingly cracking down on dissenters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 301818.0,
      "end_time": 302986.0,
      "text": "whistle-blowers"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 303100.0,
      "end_time": 304923.0,
      "text": "and investigative journalists."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 304947.0,
      "end_time": 307381.0,
      "text": "UN Secretary General Ban Ki-Moon has warned"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 307405.0,
      "end_time": 311842.0,
      "text": "that \"preventing extremism and promoting human rights go hand-in-hand.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 311866.0,
      "end_time": 314669.0,
      "text": "It's not to say that governments shouldn't keep us safe --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 314694.0,
      "end_time": 315845.0,
      "text": "of course they should --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 315869.0,
      "end_time": 318464.0,
      "text": "but we need public oversight, transparency"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 318488.0,
      "end_time": 320729.0,
      "text": "and accountability to the rule of law."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 320753.0,
      "end_time": 321905.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 321929.0,
      "end_time": 325801.0,
      "text": "extremists are literally killing off civil society in some countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 326198.0,
      "end_time": 328732.0,
      "text": "Since 2013 in Bangladesh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 328756.0,
      "end_time": 333272.0,
      "text": "over a dozen secular bloggers and community activists"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 333296.0,
      "end_time": 336229.0,
      "text": "have been literally slaughtered by extremists"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 336253.0,
      "end_time": 338597.0,
      "text": "while the government has done very little."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 339800.0,
      "end_time": 341955.0,
      "text": "From the city of Raqqa in Syria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 341979.0,
      "end_time": 346555.0,
      "text": "people like Ruqia Hassan and Naji Jerf have been assassinated"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 346579.0,
      "end_time": 349594.0,
      "text": "for their reporting out of ISIS-controlled territory."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 350315.0,
      "end_time": 355899.0,
      "text": "The citizen media group called Raqqa is Being Slaughtered Silently"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 355923.0,
      "end_time": 360142.0,
      "text": "relies on strong encryption to send out their reports"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 360166.0,
      "end_time": 363578.0,
      "text": "and shield themselves from interception and surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 364570.0,
      "end_time": 366807.0,
      "text": "Yet authorities in countries like the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 366831.0,
      "end_time": 369374.0,
      "text": "the United Kingdom and many other democracies"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 369398.0,
      "end_time": 371251.0,
      "text": "are seeking to use the law"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 371275.0,
      "end_time": 375732.0,
      "text": "to either weaken or outright ban strong encryption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 375756.0,
      "end_time": 377936.0,
      "text": "because the bad guys are using it, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 378465.0,
      "end_time": 382724.0,
      "text": "We have got to fight for the right of citizens to use strong encryption."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 382749.0,
      "end_time": 386379.0,
      "text": "Otherwise, dissent and investigative journalism"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 386403.0,
      "end_time": 388802.0,
      "text": "are going to become even more difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 388826.0,
      "end_time": 390290.0,
      "text": "in even more places."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 390654.0,
      "end_time": 393125.0,
      "text": "And the bad guys -- the criminals and terrorists --"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 393149.0,
      "end_time": 395409.0,
      "text": "are still going to find ways to communicate."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 395433.0,
      "end_time": 398720.0,
      "text": "Kudos to the companies that are standing up"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 398960.0,
      "end_time": 400550.0,
      "text": "for their users' right to use encryption."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 401595.0,
      "end_time": 403861.0,
      "text": "But when it comes to censorship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 403885.0,
      "end_time": 406195.0,
      "text": "the picture is much more troubling."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 406610.0,
      "end_time": 408428.0,
      "text": "Yes, there's a real problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 408452.0,
      "end_time": 411715.0,
      "text": "of extremist content spreading all over the internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 411739.0,
      "end_time": 415272.0,
      "text": "And Facebook, YouTube and Twitter are among the many companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 415296.0,
      "end_time": 419723.0,
      "text": "who report having taken down hundreds of thousands of pieces of content"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 419747.0,
      "end_time": 421327.0,
      "text": "and deactivating accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 421351.0,
      "end_time": 423831.0,
      "text": "that are connected to the extremist's speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 423855.0,
      "end_time": 428175.0,
      "text": "The problem is their enforcement mechanisms are a complete black box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 428199.0,
      "end_time": 430187.0,
      "text": "and there is collateral damage."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 430211.0,
      "end_time": 432929.0,
      "text": "Take, for example, Iyad el-Baghdadi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 433516.0,
      "end_time": 436152.0,
      "text": "an activist who makes fun of ISIS on Twitter."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 436176.0,
      "end_time": 437991.0,
      "text": "He had his account deactivated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 438160.0,
      "end_time": 441541.0,
      "text": "because he shares a surname with a prominent ISIS leader."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 442220.0,
      "end_time": 443371.0,
      "text": "Last December,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 443395.0,
      "end_time": 445140.0,
      "text": "a number of women named Isis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 445380.0,
      "end_time": 448490.0,
      "text": "which also happens to be the name of an Egyptian goddess,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 448514.0,
      "end_time": 450397.0,
      "text": "had their accounts deactivated."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 450742.0,
      "end_time": 452358.0,
      "text": "And this woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 452382.0,
      "end_time": 455487.0,
      "text": "who lives in the United States and is a computer programmer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 455511.0,
      "end_time": 459237.0,
      "text": "reported on Twitter about her deactivation on Facebook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 459261.0,
      "end_time": 462954.0,
      "text": "managed to get enough media attention to have her account reinstated."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 462978.0,
      "end_time": 465666.0,
      "text": "But that's the thing -- she had to get media attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 466200.0,
      "end_time": 467529.0,
      "text": "And journalists aren't immune."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 467553.0,
      "end_time": 468727.0,
      "text": "David Thomson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 468751.0,
      "end_time": 472149.0,
      "text": "an expert on terrorism and reporter for Radio France International,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 472173.0,
      "end_time": 475736.0,
      "text": "had reports deleted from his Facebook account"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 475760.0,
      "end_time": 478549.0,
      "text": "and had his account deactivated for several days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 478573.0,
      "end_time": 482474.0,
      "text": "because they contained pictures of ISIS flags,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 482498.0,
      "end_time": 484554.0,
      "text": "even though he was just reporting on ISIS,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 484578.0,
      "end_time": 485756.0,
      "text": "not promoting it."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 486253.0,
      "end_time": 489241.0,
      "text": "And then we have stories from people like this Egyptian man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 489266.0,
      "end_time": 490883.0,
      "text": "Ahmed Abdellahy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 490907.0,
      "end_time": 496490.0,
      "text": "who reported recently in an event in Washington DC"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 496740.0,
      "end_time": 498248.0,
      "text": "that some of his arguments with extremists --"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 498272.0,
      "end_time": 504585.0,
      "text": "he now spends his time on social media arguing with ISIS followers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 504609.0,
      "end_time": 506616.0,
      "text": "trying to get them to turn away --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 507141.0,
      "end_time": 512135.0,
      "text": "some of his arguments with these extremists get deleted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 512159.0,
      "end_time": 515207.0,
      "text": "which he believes has the effect of shielding them"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 515231.0,
      "end_time": 517117.0,
      "text": "from alternative points of view."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 518217.0,
      "end_time": 522602.0,
      "text": "It's unclear whether Facebook even knows the extent"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 522626.0,
      "end_time": 524137.0,
      "text": "of the collateral damage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 524162.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525994.0,
      "text": "or the other companies as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 526558.0,
      "end_time": 530172.0,
      "text": "But we do know that journalism, activism and public debate"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 530196.0,
      "end_time": 534316.0,
      "text": "are being silenced in the effort to stamp out extremist speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 535398.0,
      "end_time": 539639.0,
      "text": "So with these companies having so much power over the public discourse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 539663.0,
      "end_time": 541257.0,
      "text": "they need to be held accountable."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 541281.0,
      "end_time": 544161.0,
      "text": "They need to carry out impact assessment"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 544186.0,
      "end_time": 548703.0,
      "text": "to identify and fix the problems that we're clearly seeing."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 548727.0,
      "end_time": 552502.0,
      "text": "They need to be more transparent about their enforcement mechanisms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 552527.0,
      "end_time": 555929.0,
      "text": "and they need to have clear appeal and grievance mechanisms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 555953.0,
      "end_time": 558297.0,
      "text": "so people can get their content reinstated."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 558640.0,
      "end_time": 561833.0,
      "text": "Now, I've been talking for the last 10 minutes"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 561857.0,
      "end_time": 565972.0,
      "text": "about how governments and companies are making it more difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 565996.0,
      "end_time": 567332.0,
      "text": "for people like these."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 567356.0,
      "end_time": 570839.0,
      "text": "This is a picture of members of the citizen media network,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 570863.0,
      "end_time": 572140.0,
      "text": "Global Voices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 572380.0,
      "end_time": 574131.0,
      "text": "that I helped to cofound over 10 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 574155.0,
      "end_time": 576151.0,
      "text": "with my friend, Ethan Zuckerman."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 576175.0,
      "end_time": 580645.0,
      "text": "Interestingly, about 5 years ago, right after the Arab Spring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 580669.0,
      "end_time": 583326.0,
      "text": "the data scientist Gilad Lotan"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 583350.0,
      "end_time": 588267.0,
      "text": "created a network map of the people in Global Voices"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 588291.0,
      "end_time": 591213.0,
      "text": "who were heavy users of Twitter during the Arab Spring."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 591237.0,
      "end_time": 596454.0,
      "text": "And he found that many of these people served as key information nodes"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 596479.0,
      "end_time": 598343.0,
      "text": "between activists and journalists"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 598367.0,
      "end_time": 601391.0,
      "text": "throughout the Tunisian and Egyptian revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 601416.0,
      "end_time": 606127.0,
      "text": "We've got to make sure that these people not only survive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 606706.0,
      "end_time": 609192.0,
      "text": "but are able to continue to thrive."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 609216.0,
      "end_time": 610870.0,
      "text": "Many of them are still active,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 610894.0,
      "end_time": 612970.0,
      "text": "other than the ones who have gone to jail"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 612994.0,
      "end_time": 615913.0,
      "text": "or have been driven into hiding or exile."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 616668.0,
      "end_time": 618240.0,
      "text": "All around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 618510.0,
      "end_time": 621827.0,
      "text": "people who are sick and tired of fear and oppression"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 621851.0,
      "end_time": 625301.0,
      "text": "are linking up in their communities and across borders."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 625325.0,
      "end_time": 629588.0,
      "text": "We've got to do everything we can to push our governments and companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 629612.0,
      "end_time": 632548.0,
      "text": "to do a better job of protecting their rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 632572.0,
      "end_time": 634557.0,
      "text": "We've also got to be more mindful"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 634581.0,
      "end_time": 639426.0,
      "text": "about how our own personal, political, consumer and business choices"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 639450.0,
      "end_time": 642119.0,
      "text": "affect people like these around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 643112.0,
      "end_time": 645544.0,
      "text": "Also, if you follow the news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 645568.0,
      "end_time": 648836.0,
      "text": "it's pretty clear that that alone isn't going to be enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 649694.0,
      "end_time": 653454.0,
      "text": "We've got to take personal responsibility by joining --"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 653478.0,
      "end_time": 656335.0,
      "text": "or at very least, actively supporting --"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 656919.0,
      "end_time": 660439.0,
      "text": "the growing ecosystem of individuals and groups"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 660464.0,
      "end_time": 662550.0,
      "text": "who are fighting for social justice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 662574.0,
      "end_time": 664637.0,
      "text": "environmental sustainability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 664661.0,
      "end_time": 666223.0,
      "text": "government accountability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 666248.0,
      "end_time": 668125.0,
      "text": "human rights, freedom of the press"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 668149.0,
      "end_time": 669705.0,
      "text": "and a free and open internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 669729.0,
      "end_time": 671485.0,
      "text": "all around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 671509.0,
      "end_time": 676220.0,
      "text": "I believe that, ultimately, we can overcome"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 676244.0,
      "end_time": 682702.0,
      "text": "the digitally empowered networks of extremism, demagoguery and hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 683379.0,
      "end_time": 684559.0,
      "text": "But ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 685104.0,
      "end_time": 691828.0,
      "text": "we've got to do this by really beefing up the global networks"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 691852.0,
      "end_time": 693640.0,
      "text": "of citizens around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 693664.0,
      "end_time": 697444.0,
      "text": "powered by people who are working hard every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 697468.0,
      "end_time": 699233.0,
      "text": "and taking personal risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 699714.0,
      "end_time": 705164.0,
      "text": "for a future world that is more peaceful, just, open and free."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 705541.0,
      "end_time": 707700.0,
      "text": "Thanks very much for listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 707940.0,
      "end_time": 715611.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}